# Styling and Data

## Styling
This project uses Tailwind CSS for styling:
- [tailwind.config.js](mdc:tailwind.config.js) - Tailwind configuration
- [postcss.config.js](mdc:postcss.config.js) - PostCSS configuration
- [index.css](mdc:src/index.css) - Global CSS styles with Tailwind directives

Component-specific styles may be found in CSS files alongside the components, such as:
- [ProjectsCarousel.css](mdc:src/components/ProjectsCarousel.css)

## Data
Project data and other content is stored in the `/src/data` directory. This includes:
- Project information for the portfolio
- Social media links
- Other static content

## Theme
The project supports both light and dark themes:
- Theme switching is handled by the [ThemeToggle.tsx](mdc:src/components/ThemeToggle.tsx) component
- Theme is automatically detected based on user preferences and persisted between sessions
